snippet.title: PEO ACWA
snippet.description:
Welcome to the Program Executive Office, Assembled Chemical Weapons Alternatives’ (PEO ACWA) official YouTube channel. ACWA is responsible for the safe destruction of the U.S. chemical weapons stockpile stored at the Blue Grass Army Depot in Kentucky and the U.S. Army Pueblo Chemical Depot in Colorado. ACWA’s mission: destroy chemical weapons stockpile.

For more information, visit the Department of Defense Social Media user agreement at:
http://www.defense.gov/socialmedia/user-agreement.aspx.
